rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Mmmm, this place is the best on
sunny days! The breeze feels so good...
And the warm sunshine, too!

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If it weren't for the shouting I hear
sometimes, it would be perfect!

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There's these people all dressed
up in armor who seem to shout
in rhythm all the time.

rows.label: tlk42350122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know what they're doing,
but it makes it hard to take a nap!
